Dans process
Friday or Sunday - Consider the whole week. Looks at the apointments for the week, moves them from his digital calendar into his written daily planner. Then he asks what are my top 3 goals for the week? Then he enteres his specific tasks, and places them on his written daily calendar strategically based on what is already there. 

